              </a>
              <a href="#styles" class="btn btn-secondary sm:mb-0">
                Explore Collection
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative m-auto max-w-5xl">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595777457583-95e059d581b8?w=1200&q=80" 
            alt="Spring Dress Collection"
            class="mx-auto rounded-md w-full"
            loading="eager"
            width="1024"
            height="576"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Benefits -->
  <Features
    id="styles"
    title="Why Our Spring Dresses?"
    subtitle="Timeless elegance meets modern comfort"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Breathable Fabrics',
        description: 'Lightweight cotton, linen, and silk blends keep you cool and comfortable as temperatures rise.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Versatile Styles',
        description: 'From casual sundresses to elegant maxis, find the perfect dress for work, weekend, or special events.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Trending Prints',
        description: 'Beautiful floral patterns, pastel colors, and modern geometric designs capture the essence of spring.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Flattering Fits',
        description: 'A-line, wrap, and fit-and-flare silhouettes complement every body type and personal style.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Easy Care',
        description: 'Machine-washable options make maintaining your wardrobe effortless. Look great with minimal effort.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Sustainable Choices',
        description: 'Eco-friendly and ethically sourced materials available. Look good while doing good.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Dress Types Section -->
  <Content
    title="Dress Styles for Every Occasion"
    subtitle="Find your perfect spring look"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Floral Sundresses',
        description: 'Perfect for weekend brunch, garden parties, and casual outings. Light, breezy, and effortlessly feminine.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Wrap Dresses',
        description: 'The timeless wrap silhouette flatters every figure. Dress up or down for any occasion.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Maxi Dresses',
        description: 'Elegant floor-length styles perfect for outdoor weddings, formal events, and resort vacations.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Midi Dresses',
        description: 'The perfect balance of casual and chic. Ideal for work, dinner dates, and daytime events.',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572804013309-59a88b7e92f1?w=1200&q=80',
      alt: 'Various Spring Dress Styles',
    }}
  />

  <!-- Color Trends -->
  <Features
    title="Spring 2026 Color Trends"
    subtitle="This season's hottest hues"
    columns={3}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Soft Pastels',
        description: 'Blush pink, lavender, and mint green bring a gentle, romantic feel to your wardrobe.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Earth Tones',
        description: 'Terracotta, olive, and sand create an organic, grounded aesthetic.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Bold Accents',
        description: 'Vibrant coral, sunny yellow, and electric blue add statement-making pops of color.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Fabric Guide -->
  <Content
    title="Premium Fabrics for Spring"
    subtitle="Comfort meets sophistication"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Organic Cotton',
        description: 'Soft, breathable, and sustainable. Perfect for everyday wear and sensitive skin.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Linen Blend',
        description: 'Natural texture and excellent airflow. Gets better with every wash.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Silk & Satin',
        description: 'Luxurious sheen and drape. Elevates any look for special occasions.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Jersey Knit',
        description: 'Stretchy, comfortable, and wrinkle-resistant. Ideal for travel and busy lifestyles.',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518622358385-8ea7d0794bf6?w=1200&q=80',
      alt: 'Spring Fashion Fabrics',
    }}
    reverse={true}
  />

  <!-- Occasion Guide -->
  <Features
    title="Dresses for Every Spring Occasion"
    subtitle="From casual to formal"
    columns={2}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Office Ready',
        description: 'Professional styles in solid colors and subtle patterns. Command attention in meetings.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Date Night',
        description: 'Romantic dresses with flattering silhouettes. Make a lasting impression.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Weekend Casual',
        description: 'Effortless sundresses and shirt dresses. Perfect for shopping, lunch, and outdoor events.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Special Events',
        description: 'Statement pieces for weddings, galas, and celebrations. Stand out from the crowd.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Styling Tips -->
  <Content
    title="Style Your Spring Dress"
    subtitle="Pro tips for every look"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Layer Smartly',
        description: 'Add a denim jacket or lightweight cardigan for cool mornings. Remove as temperature rises.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Accessorize Right',
        description: 'Statement jewelry, scarves, and belts transform simple dresses into complete outfits.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Footwear Matters',
        description: 'Pair with sandals, wedges, or sneakers depending on the occasion and your personal style.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Bag Selection',
        description: 'Crossbody bags for day, clutch purses for evening. Match the formality of your dress.',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558171813-4c088753af8f?w=1200&q=80',
      alt: 'Spring Dress Styling',
    }}
  />

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <Testimonials
    title="What Customers Say"
    subtitle="Real reviews from real women"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Perfect Spring Wardrobe',
        description: 'These dresses are absolutely stunning. The quality is amazing and they fit perfectly. Received so many compliments!',
        author: 'Jessica T.',
        avatar: 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg',
      },
      {
        title: 'Comfortable & Chic',
        description: 'Finally, dresses that look expensive but feel like pajamas. Perfect for my busy schedule.',
        author: 'Amanda R.',
        avatar: 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/33.jpg',
      },
      {
        title: 'Great Quality',
        description: 'The fabric quality exceeded my expectations. Washed beautifully and still looks new after multiple wears.',
        author: 'Sarah L.',
        avatar: 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg',
      },
      {
        title: 'Perfect Fit',
        description: 'True to size and very flattering. The wrap dress is now my go-to for both work and weekend.',
        author: 'Michelle K.',
        avatar: 'https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/90.jpg',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Size & Fit Guide -->
  <Features
    title="Size & Fit Guide"
    subtitle="Find your perfect fit"
    columns={2}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'True to Size',
        description: 'Most customers find their regular size fits perfectly. Check our detailed size chart.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Curvy Options',
        description: 'Special cuts and sizes designed for curvier figures. Every body is beautiful.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Petite & Tall',
        description: 'Special length options available. No more alterations needed.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Easy Returns',
        description: 'Free returns within 30 days. Shop with confidence.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    items={[
      {
        question: 'What is the best fabric for spring dresses?',
        description: 'Lightweight fabrics like cotton, linen, and jersey knit are ideal for spring. They breathe well and keep you comfortable as temperatures fluctuate.',
      },
      {
        question: 'How do I care for my spring dresses?',
        description: 'Most spring dresses can be machine washed on gentle cycle. Always check the care label. Air dry or tumble dry low to maintain quality.',
      },
      {
        question: 'Can I wear these dresses to work?',
        description: 'Absolutely! Our collection includes many professional styles suitable for office wear. Pair with a blazer for a polished look.',
      },
      {
        question: 'What accessories go with spring dresses?',
        description: 'Depends on the occasion! Add a denim jacket and sneakers for casual days, or statement jewelry and heels for evening events.',
      },
      {
        question: 'Do you offer petite and plus sizes?',
        description: 'Yes! We offer a wide range of sizes from XS to 3XL, including petite and tall lengths where available.',
      },
      {
        question: 'What is your return policy?',
        description: 'We offer free returns within 30 days of purchase. Items must be unworn with tags attached.',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <CallToAction
    title="Ready to Bloom This Spring?"
    subtitle="Shop our exclusive spring collection. Limited stock available in popular styles."
    actions={[
      { variant: 'primary', text: 'Buy on Amazon ðŸŽ', href: 'https://amzn.to/40viXzb', target: '_blank' },
    ]}
  />
</Layout>

